<LP>
   STAR TECHNOLOGIES Inc. (Sterling, Va.) -- Robert C.
Compton, 43 years old, president and chief executive officer
of this maker of high-performance computer products, assumed
the additional post of chairman. He succeeds Herbert S. Shaw,
57, who will remain a director. The board also accepted the
resignations of Ralph R. Shaw and J. Robert Newton, reducing
board membership to four. No successors were appointed.
</LP>
