<LP>
   PRIMERICA Corp. (Greenwich, Conn.) -- This
financial-services concern named Daniel J. McAthie to the new
post of vice president and treasurer of Fingerhut Cos., its
70%-owned direct-mail marketing unit in Minneapolis. Mr.
McAthie had been vice president and treasurer of CVN Cos., a
direct-marketing company in Minneapolis acquired last fall by
QVC Network Inc., a West Chester, Pa., television retail
merchandiser.
