   MANUFACTURERS HANOVER Corp. (New York) -- John D. Zutter
Jr., executive vice president of this banking company, was
named country manager, overseeing all of the corporation's
operations in Britain. Mr. Zutter was previously in charge of
the global financial-institutions division.
</LP>
